mistral.reason: Sky Italia was launched in 2003, but it was formed from the merger of two existing companies (Telepiu and Stream) which were founded before 2003.

gemma2.reason: Multiple sources state Sky Italia was founded in 2003 as a result of the merger of Telepiu and Stream.

llama3.1.reason: The claim is wrong because Sky Italia was founded in 2003, but the merged result of Telepiu (founded in 1991) and Stream TV.
